  "title": "Legal Executive / Paralegal",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for Legal Executives / Paralegals to join our high performing team. Those who are effectively bilingual (Chinese & English) will have an advantage.</p><p></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>• Responsible for day-to-day handling of the case files and providing full secretarial support to the lawyers;</p><p>• Able to handle e-Litigation;</p><p>• Able to handle clients;</p><p>• Drafting legal correspondence and Court Documents;</p><p>• Conducting legal research; and</p><p>• Other ad-hoc administrative duties.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>• Candidates applying for Legal Executives / Paralegals should possess diploma or degree in law;</p><p>• Candidate must be able to use Microsoft Office and Excel;</p><p>• Good command of spoken and written English;</p><p>• Candidate must be organised, meticulous and hard-working; and</p><p>• Experience in litigation preferred.</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates are invited to email your comprehensive resume with a recent photo stating the availability date and expected salary to <u>yongtong@gurbaniandco.com</u>/<u>govin@gurbaniandco.com</u>.</p><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p>Thank you for applying.</p>",
