    "description": "<p>Gurbani &amp; Co LLC is a Singapore law firm which was founded in 1989. In its 32 years of business, Gurbani &amp; Co has established itself as one of the leading firms of excellence in Singapore in its main areas of practice, involving all aspects of shipping, all forms of marine and general insurance, reinsurance, international and domestic commercial arbitration and litigation. &nbsp;The leading partners of this niche practice have won the support of a solid and international and local commercial client base, constantly engaging it as the firm of ultimate choice.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Its partners have acted as arbitrators and counsel in large-scale domestic and international institutional and ad-hoc arbitrations.</p>\n<p>It has strong networks in the insurance, maritime and international trade sectors, as well as within the international arbitral community, which enables it to service the needs of its expanding client base in an increasingly global community.</p>",
